title: IE100: The most powerful Indians in 2022 - The Indian Express
content: IE100: The most powerful Indians in 2022  The Indian ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: As the PM now for eight years, Modi remains disruptor-in-chief with a regularity that expands his presence and crimps his critics. Be it the vaccination programme after the brutal second wave or, most recently, the airlift of over 22,000 young Indians from Europe, the PM has come to stand as the veritable Prime Mover.
